snippet.title: Inkslinger - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the release trailer with gameplay for “Inkslinger” -- a story-driven, Romancepunk tragedy with typing-game mechanics.

Release date: April 8, 2021.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1510410/Inkslinger/ 
Find us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/gatewaystories


Credits:
Music: Préludes Op. 28, No. 19 in E-Flat Major: Vivace by Chopin. Performed by Jeannette Fang.
Art: SMK Open.

Developed by:
Jacob Hvid Amstrup
Lucas A. V. Møller
